### Cute Bot
The Best Discord Bot

### Features
-Kick Feature.
-c!say Command to make the bot says anything. 
-More Commands are coming

### About
Cute Bot is mostly written in Java/Kotlin and his code is maintained on GitHub.
Cute Bot is a side-project written by XeZe Force.
The former is the serious one and the latter is the sarcastic one.

### So what are you waiting for!
Invite Cute Bot to your server now by this link: https://discordapp.com/oauth2/authorize?permissions=2146958455&scope=bot&client_id=245526612869775360

### Support or Contact
